text: Lyuben Obretenov (1 July 1918 - 2 May 2011) was a Bulgarian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1918 births Category:2011 deaths Category:Bulgarian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Bulgaria Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
